### Get all events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events

### Get event by ID (Replace `eventId` with an actual ID)
@eventId = 12345
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events/{{eventId}}

### Create a new event
POST http://localhost:8080/api/events
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": "12345",
    "name": "Spring Boot Conference",
    "organizerId": "5678",
    "date": "2025-06-01",
    "location": "Bucharest",
    "description": "An event about Spring Boot best practices."
}

### Update an existing event (Replace `eventId` with an actual ID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/events/{{eventId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Updated Spring Boot Conference",
    "organizerId": "5678",
    "date": "2025-06-02",
    "location": "Cluj-Napoca",
    "description": "Updated details for the event."
}

### Delete an event by ID (Replace `eventId` with an actual ID)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/events/{{eventId}}

### Get event by event name (Replace `eventName` with an actual name)
@eventName = Spring Boot Conference
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events/eventName/{{eventName}}

### Get events by organizer ID (Replace `organizerId` with an actual ID)
@organizerId = 5678
GET http://localhost:8080/api/events/organizer/{{organizerId}}
